    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to safety.incident. Business justification: Insurance claims in construction are triggered by specific safety incidents. Linking the insurance policy register to the triggering incident supports workers\' compensation processing, insurer notific' ;
    rdfs:domain ind:Construction ;
